description: Cold War 寒戰 Traditional 寒戰 Simplified 寒战 Hon zin (original title) World Premiere: October 4, 2012 (Busan International Film Festival) Release Date: October 18, 2012 Runtime: 1h 42min Genre: Action, Crime, Mystery, Police Language: Cantonese Country: Hong Kong Five police officers in Hong Kong are kidnapped. The police commissioner is on a business trip overseas. Two vice commissioners, Sean Rau and M.B. Lee, then take over the case. The two vice commissioners are rivals who both vie for the police commissioner seat. At first, M.B. Lee takes the lead in the case, but comes to a dead end. Sean Rau then takes the lead, but he falls into a trap. Both men are then investigated by the ICAC (Independent Commission Against Corruption). https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2186715/ https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cold_War_(2012_film) http://asianwiki.com/Cold_War
